 of deaf people turning on

00:01:33.392 --> 00:01:35.061
 their cochlear implants
 for the first time

00:01:35.094 --> 00:01:36.562
 and everybody gets
 all emotional?

00:01:36.595 --> 00:01:38.498
 Like, I realize we never got
 a chance to do that,

00:01:38.531 --> 00:01:40.199
 and I've always been
 kind of disappointed.

00:01:40.232 --> 00:01:42.468
 Do you think we could try it?
 - Okay...

00:01:42.501 --> 00:01:44.704
 - Okay, now fake turn it on.

